{"type":"message","id":"bf44b0d0","parentId":"52ce4e70","timestamp":"2026-03-01T13:14:29.132Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"浏览器启动了。现在需要导航到小红书。根据之前的经验，不能直接用 URL 导航，要从首页正常点击进去。但我可以先 navigate 到小红书首页看看。\n\n让我先导航到小红书，然后 snapshot 看看页面情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ba7d5bfd29f544979f5c31ea","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","url":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":21110,"output":146,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21256,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772370867233}}
