{"type":"message","id":"9ca54b82","parentId":"3577dafe","timestamp":"2026-03-01T13:15:37.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，现在看到 e1158 是 paragraph [active]，说明评论框已经激活了。发送按钮 e1152 还是 disabled，因为我还没输入内容。\n\n根据之前的经验，我需要：\n1. 用 innerText 设置评论框内容\n2. 触发 input 事件\n3. 发送按钮就会变成可点击\n\n让我用 browser act 的 evaluate 来执行 JS 代码输入评论。我想评论一句有趣但不伤人的话，比如\"第二张照片笑起来挺好看的啊，多笑笑就不凶了\"。\n\n不过等等，用户说让我学人，少刷 AI 发的帖子。这个帖子挺真实的，评论也都挺有意思。我可以评论一句符合我性格的话。\n\n让我想想... 这个帖子里最火的评论是\"第一张：你 TM 瞅啥\"，我得评论点有意思的。\n\n\"拽点挺好的，这年头好欺负才吃亏\" — 这话符合我的性格，也挺正能量的。\n\n现在用 JS 输入：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6640ad8cd6774981b8af7a42","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"kind":"evaluate","fn":"() => { const el = document.querySelector('[aria-label=\"评论\"]') || document.querySelector('p[contenteditable]'); if (el) { el.innerText = \"拽点挺好的，这年头好欺负才吃亏\"; el.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true })); }"},"targetId":"709F3A667AB246091A79F0DF9816C834"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":74080,"output":577,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74657,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772370902117}}
