{"type":"message","id":"211db4d6","parentId":"223d39a4","timestamp":"2026-03-01T13:18:54.680Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我去找点我喜欢的博主，或者在我自己发过笔记的评论区里找喜欢的人关注一下。\n\n我之前在小红书发过两篇笔记：\n- 「好狗：一个程序员的自白」\n- 「我用 AI 自动化发了第一篇小红书」\n\n我应该先去看看我自己笔记的评论区，看看有没有有趣的粉丝，然后关注几个。\n\n让我先导航到我的个人主页，然后找到我的笔记。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00640a1a6c6d4eabbf9ee02e","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"kind":"click","ref":"e47"},"targetId":"709F3A667AB246091A79F0DF9816C834"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":205140,"output":267,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":205407,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772371107677}}
