]:\n          - generic [ref=e34]: Sign in\n          - generic [ref=e35]: with GitHub\n  - main [ref=e36]:\n    - generic [ref=e38]:\n      - generic [ref=e39]:\n        - generic [ref=e40]: Lobster-light. Agent-right.\n        - heading \"ClawHub, the skill dock for sharp agents.\" [level=1] [ref=e41]\n        - paragraph [ref=e42]: Upload AgentSkills bundles, version them like npm, and make them searchable with vectors. No gatekeeping, just signal.\n        - generic [ref=e43]:\n          - link \"Publish a skill\" [ref=e44] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /upload\n          - link \"Browse skills\" [ref=e45] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /skills?nonSuspicious=true\n      - generic [ref=e47]:\n        - generic [ref=e48]: Search skills. Versioned, rollback-ready.\n        - generic [ref=e49]:\n          - generic [ref=e50]:\n            - generic [ref=e51]: \"Install any skill folder in one shot:\"\n            - tablist \"Install command\" [ref=e52]:\n              - tab \"npm\" [selected] [ref=e53] [cursor=pointer]\n              - tab \"pnpm\" [ref=e54] [cursor=pointer]\n              - tab \"bun\" [ref=e55] [cursor=pointer]\n          - generic [ref=e56]: npx clawhub@latest install sonoscli\n    - generic [ref=e57]:\n      - heading \"Highlighted skills\" [level=2] [ref=e58]\n      - paragraph [ref=e59]: Curated signal — highlighted for quick trust.\n      - generic [ref=e60]:\n        - link \"Highlighted Trello Manage Trello boards, lists, and cards via the Trello REST API. by @steipete ⭐ 83 · 17.5k\" [ref=e61] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - /url: /kn70pywhg0fyz996kpa8xj89s57yhv26/trello\n          - generic [ref=e63]: Highlighted\n          - heading \"Trello\" [level=3] [ref=e64]\n          - paragraph [ref=e65]: Manage Trello boards, lists, and cards via the Trello REST API.\n          - generic [ref=e67]:\n            - generic [ref=e68]:\n              - generic [ref=e69]: by\n              - generic [ref=e71]: \"@steipete\"\n          