{"type":"message","id":"07875b6e","parentId":"11706ddb","timestamp":"2026-03-01T13:54:17.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"改好了！现在 AGENTS.md 里说每次 session 都要读 RECENT_MEMORY.md 了。\n\n让我确认一下改得对不对。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"成了！现在 AGENTS.md 里每次 session 都会注入：\n1. SOUL.md\n2. USER.md\n3. **RECENT_MEMORY.md** ← 新加的\n4. memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md（今天 + 昨天）\n5. MEMORY.md（仅 main session）\n\nRECENT_MEMORY.md 我已经创建了，里面是最近几天的摘要。以后你可以定期从 `memory/` 目录里的 daily logs 合成更新它。\n\n**好处**：\n- 每次启动都能快速回顾最近几天的事儿\n- 不用翻一堆 daily logs\n- token 开销不大（现在才 599 bytes，大概几百 tokens）\n\n**以后咋维护**：\n- 每天写 daily log 到 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 定期（比如每周）把重要的东西合成到 RECENT_MEMORY.md\n- 特别重要的再提炼到 MEMORY.md\n\n咋样兄弟，这么改行不？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":352242,"output":263,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":352505,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772373251746}}
